Heading3: How to construct effective company Compensation Philosophy

Paragraph: Incentives and support for your employees are the two main reasons that will heighten your company’s growth. Practice bringing a different work culture in which your employees feel easy to work. Keep a balance between the incentives of the company and employees to ensure a better productivity rate.

Universities play a crucial role in underpinning innovation and entrepreneurial activities. That is why at Namal we provide the conditions, facilities that are conducive to fostering innovative ideas. In this regard, Namal's Office of Research Innovation and Commercialization hosted a Seminar on Entrepreneurship to support the development of new ideas among the student body. Mr. Hassan Syed was invited from Pakistan's largest incubation platform and the seminar was attended by a large number of students.
